WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.000
By working every day

00:01.000 --> 00:12.000
If you sit to write music once a day for at least 30 mins, you'll get into the habit of having to do something even if you think you're not inspired

00:12.000 --> 00:18.000
It's actually harder to sit down to work every day than it is to write something

